en.purpose: Example template for demonstrating how to use the Laboratory test result archetype for simple lab results.
en.use: For example use, for demonstrating how to use the Laboratory test result archetype for simple lab results. Laboratory analytes are coded using SNOMED CT. No elements have been constrained out. An oral glucose tolerance test (OGTT) has been used as the example use case.
